\section{Observations and Data Reduction}
\label{obs}

The observations were taken with the {\sl XMM-Newton}{}~EPIC-pn and EPIC-MOS cameras in Small Window mode, with the source in the field of view of the pn camera and the MOS cameras. The pn camera was operated in timing mode with the optical blocking filter in place, and the MOS cameras were operated in full frame mode. The observations were taken in the 2015 campaign, with the first observation on 2015-04-21 14:18:34 UT and the second one on 2015-04-30 13:52:02 UT. The exposure times were 12.4~ks and 13.1~ks, respectively. The data were processed with the Science Analysis System (SAS) v.15.0.0, using the standard procedures.

